{"tid":937100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陸頌雄：不少港人都有2本以上護照　鄧家彪斥反對派不講「越境捉人」","createTime":"2018-12-11T09:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T15:31:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":61,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"050f078727b80142a29a99994c30c6a6b0c3d6c4","tid":937100,"uid":39464,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181211/s00001/1cc486d2f633cfb0a8d3adba2e708eb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181211%2Fs00001%2F1cc486d2f633cfb0a8d3adba2e708eb1.jpg&h=6d6e010e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為首席財務官孟晚舟案，美國司法部文件披露孟晚舟持3本香港特區護照，但未有交代是否同時有效。特首林鄭月娥今早出席行政會議前明言，在任何時候，孟晚舟只持有一本有效特區護照。工聯會多名成員則繼續在facebook講述事件。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會立法會議員陸頌雄下午於fb發帖指要解答案中「常見問題」，其中談到「孟晚舟持有3本特區護照，是否合法」，他指「不少香港人都2本以上的護照」，又說今次事件涉及香港居民權益受損，「主謀是美國」，工聯會亦已前往美國駐港總領事館示威，批評「一眾反對派包括公民黨、新民主同盟等，至今未為孟晚舟發聲，反而將矛頭指向孟晚舟『護照問題』」<br />\n<br />\n工聯會區議員鄧家彪指摘反對派未有講「美國打壓華為」、「越境捉人」，卻說「受害者」持有多個護照，「不停係不停轉移視線，唯美國是首做遮醜布，路人皆見」。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會另一立法會議員郭偉强則形容「美加癲咗」，稱「有中國人被綁架，只因美國在商業競爭上已走向滑落，才以橫蠻之舉打擊對手」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20181211/s00001/1544517761223/【華為孟晚舟案】陸頌雄-不少港人都有2本以上護照-鄧家彪斥反對派不講「越境捉人」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20181211%2Fs00001%2F1544517761223%2F%E3%80%90%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E6%A1%88%E3%80%91%E9%99%B8%E9%A0%8C%E9%9B%84-%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%91%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%892%E6%9C%AC%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E8%AD%B7%E7%85%A7-%E9%84%A7%E5%AE%B6%E5%BD%AA%E6%96%A5%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%B4%BE%E4%B8%8D%E8%AC%9B%E3%80%8C%E8%B6%8A%E5%A2%83%E6%8D%89%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8D&d=cvk3KmuFUp%2BbMT97WyLi8kkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=6427172e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20181211%2Fs00001%2F1544517761223%2F%E3%80%90%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E6%A1%88%E3%80%91%E9%99%B8%E9%A0%8C%E9%9B%84-%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%91%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%892%E6%9C%AC%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E8%AD%B7%E7%85%A7-%E9%84%A7%E5%AE%B6%E5%BD%AA%E6%96%A5%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%B4%BE%E4%B8%8D%E8%AC%9B%E3%80%8C%E8%B6%8A%E5%A2%83%E6%8D%89%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8D&h=ce1b26e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20181211/s00001/1544517761223/【華為孟晚舟案】陸頌雄-不少港人都有2本以上護照-鄧家彪斥反對派不講「越境捉人」</a>"},{"pid":"b09d70acff7c21154fb3d95dcfae09e9071d8006","tid":937100,"uid":57723,"like":381,"dislike":0,"score":381,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:40:13.000Z","msg":"唔好理兩條on9 <br />\n就唔會有人報導<br />\n完"},{"pid":"741fb803d5c9bb7fce13c9dc4546b8763a893643","tid":937100,"uid":11719,"like":192,"dislike":1,"score":191,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:40:22.000Z","msg":"龍門已經搬到去第二個星系"},{"pid":"383d914f7e9e4afb2586523de01b480fe6aae7ea","tid":937100,"uid":179775,"like":301,"dislike":0,"score":301,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實有幾白痴先會信佢講野<br />\n<br />\n不少香港人係2本唔同地方既護照<br />\n家下佢係同一個地方有3本<br />\n<br />\n咩叫越境捉人...咩叫引導呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係唔係認真左"},{"pid":"5c5e4b64d087faf1a0a32dfc39e7b48143bba809","tid":937100,"uid":77196,"like":211,"dislike":0,"score":211,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:44:39.000Z","msg":"加拿大係加拿大國境捉人都越境<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048dd76c7ee4c74a5e4678fef5f17dd049778300","tid":937100,"uid":19527,"like":92,"dislike":0,"score":92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:45:17.000Z","msg":"有中國人被綁架，只因美國在商業競爭上已走向滑落，才以橫蠻之舉打擊對手」。<br />\n<br />\n多謝提供笑話"},{"pid":"0c946a56d77d7e3cd5b229294f93474356c1150d","tid":937100,"uid":693,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:45:41.000Z","msg":"弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\